<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare,Products.Analyzer,Products.Lingo">
    <body>
        <p>Opens the Select Remote for Pull dialog, which lets you select the remote repository from which you will download remote files. After you select the repository you want to pull from, the remote files are retrieved from the repository and downloaded to your local project.</p>
        <p>If necessary, <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> will perform a commit before pulling your files.</p>
        <p>You will see this option if your project is bound to Git.</p>
        <p>See <MadCap:xref href="../../../Source_Control/Git/Pulling_Files_from_a_Remote.htm">Pulling Files from a Remote Repository</MadCap:xref>.</p>
    </body>
</html>